# 止蝕  
(pos:動詞)  
<explanation>  
yue: 停止虧損；喺投資或生意上唔再繼續損失金錢（量詞：個）  
eng: to stop losing money; to cut losses  
<eg>  
yue: 佢見勢唔對，就決定止蝕，唔好再捱蝕。 (keoi5 gin3 si4 m4 do1, ze2 daai2 zik1 zi2 sik1, m4 hou2 zoi2 go2 joi4 sik1.)  
eng: He saw the situation wasn't good, so he decided to cut his losses and stop taking further losses. [end of text]


